ace_104rht1665702724463.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rht1665702724463.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rht1665702724463.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rht1665702724463\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      LDAP Connector Options\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"rht1665702724463__ldap_connector_options_153568\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">You can assign LDAP connector options using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$LDP_PARAMS</span> setting in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"rht1665702724463__topic_d51188e1_d51189e1_d51190e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rht1665702724463__p_d51191e1_d51192e1_d51193e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$LDP_PARAMS</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> }<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var>\n            n}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rht1665702724463__topic_d33622e1_d33623e1_d33624e1_d33625e1_d33626e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d885139e77\">\n                        \n Options\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rht1665702724463__li_d24392e1_d24393e1_d24394e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ymf1665702724534.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ymf1665702724534.html\" title=\"Determine whether the searchbase should be appended to the user DN at bind time.\">addbase</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rht1665702724463__li_d24395e1_d24396e1_d24397e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xek1665702724607.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xek1665702724607.html\" title=\"Specifies the case to be used when Uniface writes entry and attribute names into the LDAP directory.\">identifier case</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rht1665702724463__li_d24398e1_d24399e1_d24400e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tfh1665702724680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tfh1665702724680.html\" title=\"Set the maximum number of seconds to wait for search results.\">logon timeout</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rht1665702724463__li_d24401e1_d24402e1_d24403e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"spo1665702724795.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/spo1665702724795.html\" title=\"Specifies how to handle null values when storing data.\">nulldefault</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rht1665702724463__li_d24404e1_d24405e1_d24406e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wbu1665702724873.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wbu1665702724873.html\" title=\"Set the range of the search.\">searchscope</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rht1665702724463__li_d24407e1_d24408e1_d24409e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ezl1665702724946.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ezl1665702724946.html\" title=\"Set the number of entries are selected in one step of a stepped hitlist.\">stepsize</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rht1665702724463__li_d24410e1_d24411e1_d24412e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tya1665702725016.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tya1665702725016.html\" title=\"On Unix, specify the location of the CA certificate used to validate the LDAP server.\">tls ca file | directory</a> (Unix only)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rht1665702724463__li_d24413e1_d24414e1_d24415e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ldo1665702725085.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ldo1665702725085.html\" title=\"Instruct the LDAP connector to connect to the LDAP server using TLS.\">tls server validation</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"osu1679559289152.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/osu1679559289152.html\" title=\"The net_profile settings defined in the Uniface ASN file helps in improving the security of the LDAP driver on UNIX.\">net_profile (UNIX only)</a></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615618\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615618\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "LDAP Connector Options Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated M